
    NICHOLAS Majola, a qualified teacher, wants to get back to work. He has been sitting at home doing nothing since October 2010. He claims he hasn’t received his salary since January 2011.Majola, from Pietermaritzburg, blamed his suffering on the principal of Nkabini Primary School, where he was teaching.“The principal gave me a letter saying I had been transferred to Inzinga Primary School in Impendle. But the principal at Inzinga said he knew nothing about the transfer. When I went back to Nkabini, the principal told me to sit at home,” he claimed. “He said there were still issues that needed to be resolved.”if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjsvgq_n1TKAQOPedhaD3XV0FJ8oJ3aswj368VzsNKEDKolv2zlVieKqaQ_q7xOt-dVz-p5uNmF0kfNolpqSIY-ikuiv6PSDbplCuGJM-ajqu2B54mkxF2jobKgLnrf4E6cpzmWDda_R6bOCfYaaZyQU9eOFH0UMbwnguUbxiVml1SzXXW5PdyySgricqqjdjToIh0uyQYyzZjGvDFCxC8EmLbR6TmAvrtqWlddZrTakWTHahqpB8vR8BZlgtEWZykfHbdAqyF_O3_5aM1BXpTkwDa5ymeWE\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzFAft_YtqsduEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
